modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds a few more [Zombie](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) Soldiers to the mix. You’ll naturally need to add these to entitygroups and whatnot.

This will likely be in the [Creature Pack](https://7daystodiemods.com/creature-packs-a-community-entity-project/), so don’t run both at the same time.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Zombie_Soldiers)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
